etry, which is\nforbidden in two dimensions. Finally, using Dyson-Schwinger equations we\ncalculate the decay of the U$_A$(1)-invariant fermion four-point function in\nsearch for a BKT phase at zero temperature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 12 Sep 2021 14:27:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Oct 2021 13:34:12 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 2 Mar 2022 11:50:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-03"}
